Rating: 4
I made this for Thanksgiving when the person who usually brings potatoes couldn't come. I put it together the night before except for the cheese. The next day I added some additional milk and stirred it up, then added the cheese and baked as directed. It was great. Only thing is I would take it out of the refrigerator at least 1/2 hour before cooking because it is very dense and takes a while to get heated thoroghly

Rating: 3
